  • public class PercentageTextColumn
extends AmpDifferentialColumn<PercentageTextCell>
    a text column which fetches its input from a normalized view (sum of percentages over an entity id = 100, no nulls, else the output will be denormalized) which contains 4 or more columns:
    1. amp_activity_id (or pledge_id)
    2. payload (text)
    3. entity_id (e.g. sector_id, donor_id etc)
    4. percentage
    All the extra columns are ignored
